<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">On 16 Jul 2025, at 2:23=E2=80=
=AFPM, David Tallot &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:david@assetrestore.co.nz">david@a=
ssetrestore.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
